#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.13/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:343
msgid "The same qualifier can be used to specify the `OidcClient` used for a `Tokens` injection:"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/2.13/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc:350
